    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this absolute gem! \ud83c\udf1f It's in total mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just left the dealership. I've babied this car from day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a flawless ride that's ready for its next adventure, you've found it! I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have\u2014come take a look and fall in love!",
