    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black. This example features the celebrated S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system that has been meticulously serviced. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The chassis is structurally perfect, having received preventative rear subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings throughout the multi-link rear suspension. This vehicle retains its factory-spec McPherson strut geometry and original cross-drilled rotors. Every mechanical component operates at peak performance, with no rod bearing wear and a flawless compression profile. A true survivor for the collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Zero accidents. Garage kept. Full maintenance records available.",
